{"tid":54402,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[太空版minecraft]有無巴打玩緊Space engineer？","createTime":"2016-12-25T13:38:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T05:11:19.000Z","uid":900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d832705b340d8216e5da32a3981101fb7d71a06","tid":54402,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:38:06.000Z","msg":"好耐之前想玩,但果陣岩岩出無咩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近steam特價,見佢又出左好多新野,74蚊就直接買左<br />\n無可否認隻game的確整得幾正,但我英文爛唔識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCreate mode都仲搞得掂,一轉生存模式就唔識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇youtube見人地慢慢挖礦砌基地砌船整得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但自己入人地server玩 降落就已經撞散自己隻船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴打玩緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者想一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ba07a717fd8d761dcc9d8c85fd8ac2c649ec5c","tid":54402,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:38:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0163d6c793b6eae82b1308a9543e3453aebffc61","tid":54402,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"聽你講好似唔錯"},{"pid":"ad2dddba481245eb8f3a057f85ddd81e66d62c10","tid":54402,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:42:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽你講好似唔錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我咩都無講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隻game認真正既,認真製作既一隻game黎<br />\n見人地上太空既大船又要搞 重力generator 又要整氣壓門同抽氣扇<br />\n仲有無人機玩<br />\n整船每一格都要燒焊先整到,但見人地可以整d自動既機械臂幫佢搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我唔識整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d047f041aca8d5bd003d30ac74d62109387cc304","tid":54402,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:47:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rBlS_bEmVXs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrBlS_bEmVXs&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=65465a68\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rBlS_bEmVXs</a><br />\n呢個係Steam workshop其中一個自動挖礦無人機既示範片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5t0H4D_GLhU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5t0H4D_GLhU&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=6f4b1022\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5t0H4D_GLhU</a><br />\n呢個係自動造船既機械臂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,2分40開始"},{"pid":"d7f3a481866fe6cab784a252515be99b633c63c8","tid":54402,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:49:02.000Z","msg":"會唔會好複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果複雜又冇中文 我玩唔嚟"},{"pid":"4020ed0cb7c2688ef38df7c6650f27ea4eb966fe","tid":54402,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:51:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會好複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果複雜又冇中文 我玩唔嚟</blockquote><br />\n講真其實真係幾複雜,如果整大船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我都玩唔黎所以先想拉多d巴打一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下有無d英文勁既巴打會玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1a9c8fec9ba098e710daa740b4db8072d519a0","tid":54402,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime